==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Enviable
<hw>En"vi*a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[From
<er>Envy</er>.]</ety> <def>Fitted to excite envy; capable of awakening
an ardent desire to posses or to resemble.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>One of most <qex>enviable</qex> of human beings.</q>
<rj><qau>Macaulay.</qau></rj></p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>En"vi*a*ble*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos> --
<wf>En"vi*a*bly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Envie</ent>⟦br⟧
